  <name>NetPeek</name>
  <summary>See what's on your network</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      NetPeek is a simple network scanner that helps you
      discover active devices on your local network.

      Features:
      <li>Fast Network Scanning - Discover active devices on your network</li>
      <li>Port Scanning - Shows open ports on discovered devices</li>
      <li>Modern UI - Built with GTK4 and Libadwaita</li>
      <li>Multi-threaded - Fast concurrent scanning</li>
      <li>Flexible Input - Supports CIDR notation, IP ranges, and single IPs</li>
      <li>Automatic IP Detection - Instantly finds your local IP range</li>
    </p>
  </description>
